Files permissions/utilities/link

1) chmod (u,g,o)(+,-,=)(x,r,w) file_name : changes permission in a file
2) [sudo] chown [new user_name] file_name: changes user owner of a file
3) [sudo] chown : [new group_name] file/dir name: changes group name
4) stat file.txt: get metadata about a file
5) du -sh folder/: get folder size

